      • Root

        public Root(String name,
            String description)
        The constructor should only be used for instantiating the root. Instantiation of all other child nodes should be done via the nested classes, and must give a type argument (Being or Place). Creation should be done by the factory.
        Parameters:
        name - the name of this place or person
        description - the description associate with this name or person
